==English==

===Noun===
{{wikipediapar|Dayi method}}
'''Dayi'''

The "'''Dayi input method'''" is a text-input method for Chinese characters invented a few years after the [[Cāngjié]] input method and designed to be faster than [[Cāngjié]]. Like [[Cāngjié]], this system is based on the character shape rather than phonetics.

